s Erfordernis einer zu schreibenden Gefühlsmoral um die Frage: Dürfen Soldaten überhaupt töten?  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Mrz 2024) 4aDiskurs. 4aGeschichte des 20. Jahrhunderts. 4aGeschichtswissenschaft. 4aGewalt. 4aHermeneutik. 4aKonfliktforschung. 4aKrieg und Technik. 4aKulturgeschichte. 4aKulturtheorie. 4aMilitärgeschichte. 7aHISTORY / Social History.2bisacsh  aConflict Studies.  aCultural History.  aCultural Theory.  aHistory of the 20th Century.  aHistory.  aViolence.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102523008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2010-2013z9783110352856oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Geschichte 2010-2013z978311037073708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript: Complete eBook-Package 2013z9783110401219oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839421802423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839421802/original  a978-3-11-037073-7  transcript Highlight Collection Geschichte 2010-2013c2010d2013  a978-3-11-102523-0  transcript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-TGPb2013  aZDB-23-TSOc2010d2013